summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from M. J. Nist and Matilda Nist, his wife, of Seattle, Washington, to the City of Seattle, dated the 26th day of July, 1907, to all of Lot Eight (8) in Block Eleven 911) in Craven's Division to Green Lake, except the west ten feet thereof; all in the City of Seattle, to have and to hold for park and parkway purposes.
